conflict.description: Indicates how to handle name conflicts. Empty / 0: Refuses and returns 409 Conflict; 1: Replaces. If the file extensions are not the same, 403 Forbidden will be returned. If the files are identical, the request will be ignored and 304 Not Modified will be returned; Any / 2: Creates anyway. An index number will be added to the name.
conflict.title: Conflict
